name: RuviStyle
description:
🎡 RuviStyle 🎡

- is a stylized anime art style.

  • Great at doing full body shots with scenery. (Hires Fix is needed)

  • Great at creating landscapes.

  • Great at making upper body portraits.

What's new?

Improved lighting and colors, updated to match the original art-style intended.


✅ Recommended Parameters ✅
Sampler: Euler a: 20-30 steps.
CFG Scale: 5-7
Hires.fix: Latent, 20 steps, 0.37 to 0.45 denoising OR Latent(Nearest to Exact), 20 steps, 0.5 denoising
Clip Skip: 2
Negatives: (low quality, worst quality:1.4), (bad anatomy), (inaccurate limb:1.2), bad composition, inaccurate eyes, extra digit, fewer digits, (extra arms:1.2), (EasyNegative) OR
(EasyNegative:1.2)

Want to generate AI art for free?

My models are available on:

🌟 Yodayo

⚫ TensorArt

💜 PixAi

All of my stuff will be free to use! Support me on Kofi~ ☕
